nks to the known relation the sum over the \"critical\" column\nlengths can be expressed in terms of a contour integral in which the integrand\nis built out of certain special functions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 29 Sep 2013 22:33:23 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Oct 2013 11:12:50 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 2 Apr 2014 11:51:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-04-03"}
