s transcendental. These\nresults are extended to the case of three or more different means, and also to\nproblems where distributions are estimated using the bootstrap. The results\nhave practical interpretation in terms of the accuracy of inference for, among\nother quantities, the sum or difference of binomial proportions.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 30 Sep 2013 08:32:54 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-01"}
